        <briefdescription>
<para>Disable dsp context preservation. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The function is used to disable the preservation of dsp and agu context registers for a particular thread.</para>
<para>The <emphasis>options</emphasis> parameter indicates which register sets will not be used by the specified thread. It is used by ARC only.</para>
